 array['maintenance_record'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:015e','CAR-UAC','UAC.015(e)','Pilot competence assurance',
 'Operator must ensure each UA pilot is competent for the intended operation with required skills and regulatory knowledge.',
 array['credential','training_record'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:015f','CAR-UAC','UAC.015(f)','Controlled storage and release of UA',
 'UA must be stored securely and released for pilot use in a controlled, documented manner.',
 array['document','mission_record'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:015h','CAR-UAC','UAC.015(h)','Operational records control and 24-month retention',
 'Operator must establish procedures to control UA operation records; records protected from damage, alteration and theft, retained at least 24 months.',
