('CARUAC:015h-AMC','CAR-UAC','AMC to UAC.015(h)','Flight mission log minimum contents',
 'Flight logs must include date, route/GPS coordinates, start/end times, pilot name, observations/incidents/equipment failures, airspace approval reference, UA details (model, serial, registration, weight, colour), and pilot training certificate/licence references.',
