('CARUAC:020','CAR-UAC','UAC.020','UA pilot licensing',
 'Pilots must hold the applicable GCAA UA pilot licence for the operation conducted.',
 array['credential'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:025','CAR-UAC','UAC.025','Airspace approval per operation',
 'UA operations require applicable airspace approval; approvals must be obtained and referenced before flight.',
 array['mission_record'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:035a','CAR-UAC','UAC.035(a-c)','Accident and serious incident reporting within 3 hours',
 'Accidents and serious incidents must be reported to GCAA (and local police for accidents) within 3 hours with all pertinent information; follow-up report on preventive actions where relevant.',
