('CARUAC:035d','CAR-UAC','UAC.035(d)','Occurrence reporting via ROSI',
 'Operator must report occurrences (crashes, signal interference, near miss, collisions, public nuisance, operations outside assigned area, injuries, lost UA) to GCAA through the ROSI system.',
 array['occurrence'],'Issue 02'),
('CARUAC:040','CAR-UAC','UAC.040','UOA continued validity (annual)',
 'UA Operator Authorisation is valid for one year subject to continued compliance, valid security clearance, and authority access to facilities, equipment, documents and records at any time.',
